<h4><a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2020/07/20/apple-5g-iphones-2020-mmwave-sub-6ghz/">2021 年版 5G iPhone 或只支持单种 5G 频段</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1352768" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/iPhone-12-5G-New-1.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="450" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/iPhone-12-5G-New-1.jpg 800w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/iPhone-12-5G-New-1-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/iPhone-12-5G-New-1-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></p>
<p>MacRumors 消息，此前消息普遍认为今年秋季推出的 5G 版 iPhone 将支持 sub-6GHz 和 mmWave 毫米波两种频段。</p>
<p>DigiTimes 新报告指出，苹果在考虑将 2021 年推出的 5G iPhone 改为只支持单频段的版本。苹果将根据当地更广泛使用的 5G 频段来决定不同市场采用哪种 5G 频段，以降低成本。</p>
<h4><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/status/4528898592736549?sudaref=login.sina.com.cn">海底捞回应塑料乌鸡卷事件</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1352769" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/N1qJ-fykiufe6740511.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="836" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/N1qJ-fykiufe6740511.jpg 1280w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/N1qJ-fykiufe6740511-360x235.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/N1qJ-fykiufe6740511-768x502.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/N1qJ-fykiufe6740511-1024x669.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>
<p>36kr 消息，针对消费者在济南海底捞就餐时在乌鸡卷中吃出硬质塑料片一事，海底捞回应表示，门店于当日接到反馈便对该产品的供应商生产加工、门店配餐等过程进行全面排查，对供应商生产加工环节派食安人员到现场进行核查。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1352773" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/6a492467ly1ggxtxflhahj20u01hc4mn.jpg" alt="" width="1080" height="1920" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/6a492467ly1ggxtxflhahj20u01hc4mn.jpg 1080w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/6a492467ly1ggxtxflhahj20u01hc4mn-360x640.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/6a492467ly1ggxtxflhahj20u01hc4mn-768x1365.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/6a492467ly1ggxtxflhahj20u01hc4mn-576x1024.jpg 576w" sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px" /></p>
<p>经排查，该事件原因已确定为工厂灌装环节员工操作不规范，导致产品标签掉落到产品中。7 月 12 日，市民郑女士和同伴在济南海底捞连城广场店就餐时在乌鸡卷中吃出硬质塑料片。</p>
